    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You\u2019ve got to see this absolute gem! I\u2019m parting with my pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in such flawless condition you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and looks brand new inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s truly perfect, this is the one for you! Come say hi and take a look\u2014you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
