    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its analog purity. This S54 powerplant features a perfectly synchronized double-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including WPC-treated rod bearings and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement utilizing structural plates. The chassis remains taut with a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers and OEM-plus bushings. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec variable M-differential lock. Finished in concours-level paint with a flawless interior, this example is mechanically and aesthetically superlative.",
